OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FDry settled and warm
OL,6,FThursday and Friday with variable
OL,7,Fcloud and plenty of sunny spells. A
OL,8,Fmostly cloudy day on Saturday with
OL,9,Fshowers possible. Breezier on
OL,10,FThursday, otherwise light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,13,Fdry, bright and warm on Friday but
OL,14,Fcloudier with the chance of a shower
OL,15,Flater. Cooler and cloudier over the
OL,16,Fweekend with a chance of showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
